text:
Have fun & enjoy lots of bats and lots of frogs! As well as the levels generated by all of you!

The levels are listed in timestamp order so get your tweet out soon to be one of the early levels!
#Speclucky

When you tweet to #Speclucky, it will generate a level for you (on the next update). You can also make some request for things like more spikes!

You'll need to download the newest versions (updating frequently throughout the rating process) to get the newest levels)

Welcome to #Speclucky ! A game with all of its levels generated from tweets to the #Spelucky hashtag.

no bats no spikes no frogs
